{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"1":"Purification (Kitab Al-Taharah)"},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":390,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":390}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":104,"arabicnumber":104,"text":"حدثنا مسدد، حدثنا عيسى بن يونس، عن الاعمش، عن ابي صالح، عن ابي هريرة، عن النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم - يعني بهذا الحديث - قال مرتين او ثلاثا ولم يذكر ابا رزين","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":104}}]}